CalculatedMeasure.name: Access To Exercise Opportunities
CalculatedMeasure.Annotation: Percentage of population with adequate access to locations for physical activity
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([State Access to exercise opportunities]) THEN [State Access to exercise opportunities] ELSE [County Access to exercise opportunities] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Access To Exercise Opportunities CI Low
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cilow Access to exercise opportunities]) THEN [mea_state_cilow Access to exercise opportunities] ELSE [mea_county_cilow Access to exercise opportunities] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Obesity
CalculatedMeasure.Annotation: Percentage of adults that report a BMI of 30 or more
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_value Adult obesity]) THEN [mea_state_value Adult obesity] ELSE [mea_county_value Adult obesity] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Obesity CI Low
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cilow Adult obesity]) THEN [mea_state_cilow Adult obesity] ELSE [mea_county_cilow Adult obesity] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Obesity CI High
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cihigh Adult obesity]) THEN [mea_state_cihigh Adult obesity] ELSE [mea_county_cihigh Adult obesity] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Smoking
CalculatedMeasure.Annotation: Percentage of Adults Who Are Current Smokers
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_value Adult smoking]) THEN [mea_state_value Adult smoking] ELSE [mea_county_value Adult smoking] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Smoking CI High
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cihigh Adult smoking]) THEN [mea_state_cihigh Adult smoking] ELSE [mea_county_cihigh Adult smoking] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Adult Smoking CI Low
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cilow Adult smoking]) THEN [mea_state_cilow Adult smoking] ELSE [mea_county_cilow Adult smoking] END
